{"tid":2231960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警察扔少年落橋 被控企圖殺人罪","createTime":"2020-10-06T05:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T05:12:42.000Z","uid":50386,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7297860f6a87a4b8743fb24c2df25d367fb00e94","tid":2231960,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"智利一名16歲少年前日（3日）於首都聖地雅哥示威期間，被警員從橋上扔落淺河後重傷，事件引發全球關注。事隔1日，智利司法部門今（4日）下令拘捕該警員，當地執法部門亦表示，<span class=\"red\">該警員將會被控「意圖殺人罪」。</span><br />\n<br />\n少年事發後被送往附近的Santa Mar&iacute;a Clinic搶救，他頭部重創，情況嚴重。當地警方發言人事發後曾指少年因失平衡而自行掉落水中，未有承認警員行為。民眾於上週六（3日）示威，要求於示威期間阻撓執法機制運作的警察執行長Rozas辭職，亦對警方回應表達不滿。<span class=\"red\">智利司法部門下令拘捕該警員，當地執法部門亦表示當地執法部門今（4日）表示，當局經調查後認為該警員涉嫌將一男子推進河中，該警員將會被控「意圖殺人罪」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3d2Pl2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3d2Pl2w&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=b84d8314\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3d2Pl2w</a>"},{"pid":"d738761deae2a15fb4e5b87d1f378535508a8ef8","tid":2231960,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8cee9eea4524d3d112aa88a668cc120ba515a2","tid":2231960,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"呢啲新聞喺全世界任何一個地方都可能發生 但香港就肯定除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee70f7cfe88156694b2dce56169034896d680f1","tid":2231960,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"美國果邊警察開槍會告謀殺<br />\n<br />\n香港... <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe